snippet.textDisplay: "2 AM" is a haunting melody that delves into the depths of the human psyche, particularly when the world is asleep and thoughts run wild. With two contrasting perspectives on love and hate, the song becomes a poignant exploration of these complex emotions. "STAR SHAH" resonates with disillusionment, proclaiming love as nothing but a facade, while "ZEESHAN ALI" passionately argues for its transcendence and importance. "Coke Studio Pakistan's" visual representation of this internal struggle is truly commendable, perfectly capturing the ethereal essence of the song. Their skillful set design enhances the emotional impact, making the performance a captivating experience that lingers long after the music fades. Major props to Coke Studio Pakistan for bringing such depth and artistry to life with Lyrics.
